{"tid":168497,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]支那男突衝出馬路　鑽巴士車底遭輾爆頭","createTime":"2017-03-23T14:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T15:49:16.000Z","uid":32407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91ed5cadc75da4bf5b42a5a3831c8d626fc7a15e","tid":168497,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/bkncn-20170323054635772-0323_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170323%2Fbkncn-20170323054635772-0323_05011_001.html&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnAwKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=3be1dc14\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/bkncn-20170323054635772-0323_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/photo/bkncn-20170323054635772-0323_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170323%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170323054635772-0323_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=b049fb2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/photo/bkncn-20170323054635772-0323_05011_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170323%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170323054635772-0323_05011_001_02b.jpg&h=89c4c7ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣西南寧市昨日發生一宗離奇命案，一男一女在路邊交談時，男子趁巴士經過一刻衝出馬路，鑽進巴士車底，任由巴士輾爆其頭顱，當場死亡。女子曾一度嘗試阻止，惟最終都遲來一步，目送男子在自己旁邊被巴士輾斃，只能撫屍痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n廣西南寧市交警隊官方微博通報了此事。3月22日下午3時54分，現場為南寧市金洲路埌西綜合市場路段南往北方向。<br />\n<br />\n一名藍衣男子與一名紅衣女子在離巴士車站約20米處的行人路上交談，該男子突然從沖向準備進站的巴士車底，頭部被巴士右後輪碾壓，當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n事故發生後，南寧市公安局交警支隊指揮中心立即指派七大隊警員到場，對現場進行勘查處理，同時調看監控視頻，查找相關證據。警方沒有披露該對男女的關係，事故的原因正在進一步調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1308d130b564eed82809bb2fcfee625d887e985","tid":168497,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:49:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}